flowchart LR
    A[User sends prompt] --> B[Add user message and assistant slot]
    B --> C{Auto SFQ on?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Run background SFQ lookup]
    C -- No --> E[Skip lookup]
    D --> F[Send prompt to AI]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Stream response into chat]
    F --> H{Tool action emitted?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Show action start and done or failed]
    H -- No --> J[Continue normal response]
    I --> K[Render updated chat timeline]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Ready for next prompt]
